item.content:encoded:
Many of us breed dogs in households. Let’s look after the dog in our house like someone else. For its participation, the language will be loyal to us.


How many people don’t know we shouldn’t give dogs some nutritious food Know what this package doesn’t know.
Also like chocolate dogs. But dogs are very dangerous with chocolate. Chocolate theobromine causes dogs toxicity. In dark chocolate, dark chocolate this component is particularly high. It can make dogs diarrhea and thirsty.
Frost and fried foods such as popcorn are harmful to dogs. Excessive thirst or excessive urination can cause excess salt discomfort.
